Banking & Finance Associate
Charterhouse
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 5 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Charterhouse is working with a premier full service Banking and Finance Practice looking to hire a Banking and Finance Associate to join their award winning Practice. Our client operates across a range of clientele including major financial institutions, investment houses, corporations, large financial advice providers as well as industry groups and regulators.
Working closely as a team in this award winning Practice, you will specialise in corporate, project and property finance as well as compliance with the financial regulatory framework. You will associate closely with highly respected and talented Partners thus learning from the best. Additionally, you will deal with exclusive clients and will often work on novel and complex cases.
REQUIREMENTS
The successful candidate should have at least 3 years post qualified experience. This is an excellent prospect for candidates seeking to work for a leading Practice who are known for their accomplished employees and quality of work in the region.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
During the last ten years, Charterhouse has been operating across Dubai, Abu Dhabi and the GCC Markets. In many ways, we were the recruiter who established and set the standards within the regional recruitment industry benchmarking and innovating the service levels associated to Search and Selection.
Charterhouse understands the dynamics attached to talent acquisition, relationship management and the required service levels within the regional industry. Our heritage is now our main strength as we continue to work within our core markets to deliver key account management and strong contingency recruitment practices to our clients and candidates.
